* Programming *                -*-muse-*-

Mark is proficient in a large number of programming languages,
frameworks, and tools platforms. He is an expert in C++, C#, and
Python. 

He has written around one million lines of code in his carreer,
choosing to focus on real implementation rathers than creating Power
Point slides. His greatest joy is to turn on something cool and see it
work properly.

Mark believes in software craftsmanship.  He has been involved with
other agile software practioners to help raise the bar in software
development. 

Better software practices can lower the development cost
and increase the results delivered by any software team. It is worth
spending time and effort to achieve this goal.
